import React from 'react'
import { IonPage, IonCard, IonHeader, IonToolbar, IonBackButton, IonContent, IonTitle, IonButtons, IonTextarea,
    IonButton ,IonCardContent, IonLabel, IonItem, IonInput, IonFab, IonFabButton, IonIcon} from '@ionic/react'

import { add } from 'ionicons/icons'


export const ShowBeans = () =>{
    return(
        <IonPage>
            <IonHeader>
                <IonToolbar>
                        <IonButtons slot='start'>
                           <IonBackButton defaultHref='home'/>
                        </IonButtons>
                <IonTitle>Bohnen anzeigen</IonTitle>
                </IonToolbar>
                </IonHeader>
            <IonContent>
                <IonFab vertical='top' horizontal='center' slot='fixed'>
                    <IonFabButton color='dark'>
                        <IonIcon icon={add}/>
                    </IonFabButton>
                </IonFab>
            </IonContent>
        </IonPage>
    )
}
